\c 8
\cl CHAPTER 8
\p
\v 1 ¶ And the LORD spake unto Moses, saying,
\p
\v 2 Speak unto Aaron, and say unto him, When thou lightest the lamps, the seven lamps shall give light over against the candlestick.
\p
