\p
\v 4 And this work of the candlestick \add was of\add* beaten gold, unto the shaft thereof, unto the flowers thereof, \add was\add* beaten work: according unto the pattern which the LORD had showed Moses, so he made the candlestick.
\p
\v 5 ¶ And the LORD spake unto Moses, saying,
\p
