\p
\v 7 And thus shalt thou do unto them, to cleanse them: Sprinkle water of purifying upon them, and let them shave all their flesh, and let them wash their clothes, and \add so\add* make themselves clean.
\p
\v 8 Then let them take a young bullock with his meal offering, \add even\add* fine flour mingled with oil, and another young bullock shalt thou take for a sin offering.
\p
