\p
\v 10 And thou shalt bring the Levites before the LORD: and the children of Israel shall put their hands upon the Levites:
\p
\v 11 And Aaron shall offer the Levites before the LORD \add for\add* an offering of the children of Israel, that they may execute the service of the LORD.
\p
\v 12 And the Levites shall lay their hands upon the heads of the bullocks: and thou shalt offer the one \add for\add* a sin offering, and the other \add for\add* a burnt offering, unto the LORD, to make an atonement for the Levites.
\p
